data.description: Very well kept one level home. Hardwood floors under the carpet. Owner is painting some of the rooms. Shows really well. Some furnishings are for sale. Formal living room and family room. Nice patio off the family room. Lot to the Large pine trees are part of the property. Sheds convey. Inside pictures are coming soon. Property is very well maintained.
